    dc:description "FIGURE 5 A – F. Peristerophila lature sp. nov., female (A – C). A, peritremes; B, fan-like seta p’ of tarsi III; C, solenidia of legs I. Male (D – F). D, peritremes; E, opisthosoma in ventral view; F, dorsal view." ;
